de.hshl.obj.wavefront.obj

Interface PolygonalOBJBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TriangularOBJBuilder

    public interface PolygonalOBJBuilder
    For each line in the OBJ file, the appropriate method on an object which implements this interface will be called. All non-polygonal lines will trigger a DecodingException. Implement this interface if you want to collect the parsed information into a custom data structure other than TriangularOBJBuilder.
    Author:
    Johannes Vollmer
    See Also:
    Parser
